[section:next_to `next_to`]

[section Synopsis]
[reference__next_to]
[endsect]

[section Description]
This metafunction returns the `next` type nested in the specified type if it
is not a __Boost_TypeErasure_placeholder__.  This metafunction is safe to
instantiate with such placeholders in a __Boost_TypeErasure_deduced__ context.
[endsect]

[section:definition Where defined]
``
#include <__next_to__header__>
``

--or--

``
#include <__concept_traits__header__>
``

Forward declaration:

``
#include <__trivial_access__header_fwd__>
``

--or--

``
#include <__concept_traits__header_fwd__>
``
[endsect]

[endsect] [/ next_to]

